title: Flaska - Badass EP
description:
This is the first album of the Hungarian pirate-folk metal band called Flaska.

Mostly inpired by the well known Alestorm musicband.

The crazyness in this music is played at a very high level :)

If you have enough sense of humor or you just love folk metal music, you should listen this!
